  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/03b04b23c21415be17ef668e245ac51b.avif?t=1772017873\" width=800 height=1688 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/74e59e7b766a76ab7bd87f2d9aad2ab3.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on an epic saga in Asgard's Fall, a norse Survivors-like Roguelite. Fight your way through hordes of creatures and let the gods feel your relentless wrath. How will your saga unfold?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/da5070386c9e2f71ecbf0ff628b414a7.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can choose from a variety of heroes to demonstrate your might in the battle against Asgard, such as the fierce Warrior and the agile Huntress, each with their own distinct skill tree. Do you have the courage to face the hordes and leaders of the Nine Realms?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/9d6169e351114d7fb8344cf84b8431d2.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the art of combat with the dynamic Ability System. Choose from a diverse array of skills, each tailored to your playstyle. Unleash devastating attacks, strategic buffs, and unique powers to conquer the Nine Realms. Forge your hero's destiny!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/0c016f5ef390f1759a64a52345a2d97a.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Behold the Web of Wyrd, where the threads of destiny are woven by your own hand. Forge your fate by placing powerful knots into the Web of Wyrd, further enhancing your strength on your path to conquering Asgard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/cd89be4a2e9c4ebf0af0298b411a43cf.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A meta-progression system where you unlock Warpaint runes that modify and amplify your characters' abilities. It features an inventory management system, challenging you to fit as many effective runes as possible into a limited space, maximizing their impact on your abilities, playstyle, and strategy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warpaint runes can be found during battle or crafted using pigments looted from enemies or discovered in Yggdrasil's Gift caches.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/efc3a5953f76a31070a3fdf8bf2d8179.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape your hero's evolution with our intricate Skill Tree. Customize your playstyle by unlocking diverse abilities, enhancing strengths, and adapting to challenges. Every choice influences your saga's outcome. Craft a hero uniquely suited to your journey through the Nine Realms!</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/3074c5581659cb9c004fe74dcf337aaf.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asgard’s Fall takes streaming to the next level with interactive Twitch extension, letting viewers directly influence the action. Through real-time polls, your audience can bless you with powerful boons or challenge you with devastating twists—turning every run into an unpredictable adventure. No two playthroughs are ever the same!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/ad7b56457060f6782214d5a39698f98a.webp?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/74e59e7b766a76ab7bd87f2d9aad2ab3.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/f191b9c70dd3ddb618f9ba0ed7c294f0.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on an epic saga in Asgard's Fall, a norse Survivors-like Roguelite. Fight your way through hordes of creatures and let the gods feel your relentless wrath. How will your saga unfold?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/da5070386c9e2f71ecbf0ff628b414a7.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/26b48f3d750b006aa266077bc6492c87.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can choose from a variety of heroes to demonstrate your might in the battle against Asgard, such as the fierce Warrior and the agile Huntress, each with their own distinct skill tree. Do you have the courage to face the hordes and leaders of the Nine Realms?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/9d6169e351114d7fb8344cf84b8431d2.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/4dfe04c5330fe685b645378ee7bf5f57.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the art of combat with the dynamic Ability System. Choose from a diverse array of skills, each tailored to your playstyle. Unleash devastating attacks, strategic buffs, and unique powers to conquer the Nine Realms. Forge your hero's destiny!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/0c016f5ef390f1759a64a52345a2d97a.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/fc46c31d6ea7cad16b157c63f20b66c3.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Behold the Web of Wyrd, where the threads of destiny are woven by your own hand. Forge your fate by placing powerful knots into the Web of Wyrd, further enhancing your strength on your path to conquering Asgard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/cd89be4a2e9c4ebf0af0298b411a43cf.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/dbcad22cc3939ef916676b2a52976ffd.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A meta-progression system where you unlock Warpaint runes that modify and amplify your characters' abilities. It features an inventory management system, challenging you to fit as many effective runes as possible into a limited space, maximizing their impact on your abilities, playstyle, and strategy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warpaint runes can be found during battle or crafted using pigments looted from enemies or discovered in Yggdrasil's Gift caches.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/efc3a5953f76a31070a3fdf8bf2d8179.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/63d03cc2eda9be49fdf33c6c55f7809d.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape your hero's evolution with our intricate Skill Tree. Customize your playstyle by unlocking diverse abilities, enhancing strengths, and adapting to challenges. Every choice influences your saga's outcome. Craft a hero uniquely suited to your journey through the Nine Realms!</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/3074c5581659cb9c004fe74dcf337aaf.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asgard’s Fall takes streaming to the next level with interactive Twitch extension, letting viewers directly influence the action. Through real-time polls, your audience can bless you with powerful boons or challenge you with devastating twists—turning every run into an unpredictable adventure. No two playthroughs are ever the same!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/ad7b56457060f6782214d5a39698f98a.webp?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.poster.avif?t=1772017873\" width=616 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.webm?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/d5be7dd31988208c2266a00d5e87fbad.mp4?t=1772017873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
